### REST examples for Exolynk Order MVP

# Create order (sample)
POST https://your-instance.exolynk.app/api/order
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "client_id": "{{client_uuid}}",
  "amount_total": 9533.50,
  "state": "NEW",
  "status": "OPEN",
  "shipment_state": "PICKING",
  "payment_state": "NO"
}

# Action: sales.to_picking
POST https://your-instance.exolynk.app/api/order/{{order_id}}/actions/sales.to_picking
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{}

# Action: manager.allow_picking
POST https://your-instance.exolynk.app/api/order/{{order_id}}/actions/manager.allow_picking
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{}
